class PatternOccurrence

PatternOccurrence * -- 1 RoutineCallTrace
A RoutineCallTrace has some PatternOccurrences. It can have none, and there is no upper bound defined.
A PatternOccurrence has A RoutineCallTrace. It must always have exactly, one, and can never have none. And there is an upper bound of at most one RoutineCallTrace.
When a PatternOccurrence is created, its RoutineCallTrace must be assigned. When a PatternOccurrence is deleted, its RoutineCallTrace is not deleted and its list of PatternOccurrences is decreased.
